WEBVTT

00:01.589 --> 00:05.444
The banana is one of the favorite fruits of many people around the world.

00:09.350 --> 00:12.884
It is a sweet, yellow, fleshy fruit when it's ripe.

00:16.421 --> 00:19.671
It has an amazing smooth yellow skin called the peel.

00:23.609 --> 00:27.997
The skin can easily be removed by pulling it off part by part.

00:28.951 --> 00:30.209
Isn't that amazing?

00:30.475 --> 00:34.065
And if you watch, you'll see that monkeys too love bananas.

